<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SimpleWebServer - 홈</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="landing-page">
      <h1>SimpleWebServer에 오신 것을 환영합니다</h1>
      <p>최소한의 웹서버로 회원가입, 로그인, 로그아웃 기능을 제공합니다.</p>

      <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
        <div class="button-group">
          <a href="/main" class="btn btn-primary">대시보드로 이동</a>
          <form action="/logout" method="POST" style="display: inline;">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary">로그아웃</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <div class="button-group">
          <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary">로그인</a>
          <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-secondary">회원가입</a>
        </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
